        "content": "<p>We have more general results: <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/WeakDual.html#WeakDual.instT2Space\">WeakDual.instT2Space</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/InnerProductSpace/WeakOperatorTopology.html#ContinuousLinearMapWOT.tendsto_iff_forall_inner_apply_tendsto\">ContinuousLinearMapWOT.tendsto_iff_forall_inner_apply_tendsto</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Operator/Completeness.html#ContinuousLinearMap.isCompact_image_coe_of_bounded_of_closed_image\">ContinuousLinearMap.isCompact_image_coe_of_bounded_of_closed_image</a>.</p>\n<p>(5) should follow from <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/WeakDual.html#WeakDual.isSeqCompact_closedBall\">WeakDual.isSeqCompact_closedBall</a> and  (3) should follow from <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/LocallyConvex/WeakSpace.html#Convex.toWeakSpace_closure\">Convex.toWeakSpace_closure</a>.</p>",
